  <h3>Why accurate measurements matter</h3><p class="">Accurate measurements ensure that your product fits snugly in its packaging, preventing unnecessary movement that could lead to damage. Plus, a well-fitting box looks more professional and creates a better unboxing experience for your customers.</p><h3>Tools you’ll need</h3>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
