        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <ul data-rte-list="default"><li><p class="">A ruler or measuring tape</p></li></ul><ul data-rte-list="default"><li><p class="">Your product (soap, dropper bottle, etc.)</p></li><li><p class="">A notebook or digital tool for recording measurements</p></li></ul><h4>STEP 1</h4><h3>Measure the dimensions of your product</h3>





















  
  














































  

    

