          <figcaption data-width-ratio class="image-card-wrapper">
            

              

              
                <p class="">To create a box that fits your product perfectly, you’ll need three key measurements:</p><ol data-rte-list="default"><li><p class=""><strong>Length:</strong> measure the longest side of your product.</p></li><li><p class=""><strong>Width:</strong> measure the side that is perpendicular to the length.</p></li><li><p class=""><strong>Height:</strong> measure the vertical dimension, from the base to the highest point.</p></li></ol>
              

              

            
          </figcaption>
        

      </figure>

    

  













































  

    
  
    

      

      
