          " data-scrolled
      >

        
          
            
            
              
              
              
              
              
              
              
              <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/34995613-78d8-43b9-9009-68696002342c/nasal_dropper_8.jpg" data-image-dimensions="1628x1805" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/34995613-78d8-43b9-9009-68696002342c/nasal_dropper_8.jpg?format=1000w" width="1628" height="1805" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/34995613-78d8-43b9-9009-68696002342c/nasal_dropper_8.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/34995613-78d8-43b9-9009-68696002342c/nasal_dropper_8.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/34995613-78d8-43b9-9009-68696002342c/nasal_dropper_8.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/34995613-78d8-43b9-9009-68696002342c/nasal_dropper_8.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/34995613-78d8-43b9-9009-68696002342c/nasal_dropper_8.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/34995613-78d8-43b9-9009-68696002342c/nasal_dropper_8.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/34995613-78d8-43b9-9009-68696002342c/nasal_dropper_8.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

              
            
          
            
          

        

        
          
          <figcaption data-width-ratio class="image-card-wrapper">
            

              

              
                <p class=""><strong>Soap bars:</strong> Measure the soap after it’s fully cured since the size can shrink slightly during curing.</p><p class=""><strong>Dropper bottles:</strong> Measure the widest part of the bottle and include the height of the dropper.</p><p class=""><strong>Irregular shapes:</strong> Use a flexible measuring tape to follow the contours of your product for the most accurate results.</p>
              

              

            
          </figcaption>
        

      </figure>

    

  


<hr />


  <p class="">By following these steps, you’ll create a perfectly fitting box that protects your product and enhances your brand’s presentation. If you have any questions, feel free to reach out or browse my collection of editable box templates designed for cosmetic and skincare businesses.</p><h3>Need help resizing your box template?</h3><p class="">If you’ve found one of my editable box templates that you love but the size doesn’t quite match your product, don’t worry! I can easily resize the box dieline to perfectly fit your needs. All you have to do is send me the exact measurements of your product, and I’ll handle the rest. This way, you can enjoy a beautiful, customized packaging solution without the hassle of starting from scratch!</p>





















  
  



