  <h4><strong>2. Explore Their Portfolio</strong></h4><p class="">A designer's portfolio serves as their visual resume. When reviewing their work, look for diversity and adaptability in their brand projects. This will help you assess whether their design sensibilities align with your brand's vision.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
