        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <h4><strong>3. Discovery Call: A Must</strong></h4><p class="">A discovery call is a crucial step. It's an opportunity to gauge their approach and see if there's a mutual fit. During this call, observe how well they understand your brand and ask questions about your business goals and audience.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
