            </a>
          

        

        
          
          <figcaption data-width-ratio class="image-card-wrapper">
            

              
                <h4><strong>3. Embrace Minimalist Packaging</strong></h4>
              

              
                <p class="">Remember the age-old saying, "less is more"? Apply this principle to your packaging. Opt for simple yet elegant designs that won't break the bank. With a little creativity using labels, stickers, and other customisable elements, you can personalise standard packaging to reflect your brand's unique identity.</p>
              

              

            
          </figcaption>
        

      </figure>

    

  













































  

    

      <figure data-test="image-block-v2-outer-wrapper" class="
