          <figcaption data-width-ratio class="image-card-wrapper">
            

              
                <h4><strong>4. Make Social Media Your Runway</strong></h4>
              

              
                <p class="">Leverage the power of social media platforms like Instagram and Pinterest to showcase your brand's style and personality. Consistently post content that reflects your brand's identity and engages your target audience. As people start talking about your brand organically, your online presence will grow without the need for expensive marketing campaigns.</p>
              

              

            
          </figcaption>
        

      </figure>

    

  













































  

    

      <figure data-test="image-block-v2-outer-wrapper" class="
            sqs-block-image-figure
