            individual-text-animation-site-default
            image-position-left
            
          " data-scrolled
      >

        
          
            
            
              
              
              
              
              
              
              
              <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/1702913399128-AIDZTMQU8ROVASEBD71B/image-asset.jpeg" data-image-dimensions="2070x2500" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/1702913399128-AIDZTMQU8ROVASEBD71B/image-asset.jpeg?format=1000w" width="2070" height="2500" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/1702913399128-AIDZTMQU8ROVASEBD71B/image-asset.jpeg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/1702913399128-AIDZTMQU8ROVASEBD71B/image-asset.jpeg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/1702913399128-AIDZTMQU8ROVASEBD71B/image-asset.jpeg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/1702913399128-AIDZTMQU8ROVASEBD71B/image-asset.jpeg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/1702913399128-AIDZTMQU8ROVASEBD71B/image-asset.jpeg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/1702913399128-AIDZTMQU8ROVASEBD71B/image-asset.jpeg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/1702913399128-AIDZTMQU8ROVASEBD71B/image-asset.jpeg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

              
            
          
            
          

        

        
          
          <figcaption data-width-ratio class="image-card-wrapper">
            

              
                <h4><strong>5. Become a Branding Buff</strong></h4>
              

              
                <p class="">Take advantage of the many free or affordable online courses and webinars on branding and design. Continuously expand your knowledge and skills to become a more knowledgeable and savvy brand owner. The better understanding you have of branding, the more prepared you will be to make informed decisions and effectively communicate your brand. This will also benefit you when you are ready to work with a professional brand designer.</p>
              

              

            
          </figcaption>
        

      </figure>

    

  





  <h4><strong>6. Your Customers, Your Consultants</strong></h4><p class="">Engage with your early customers and seek their feedback on your branding. Their insights can be invaluable in steering your brand in the right direction, all without the hefty fees of a professional consultant. Listen to your customers' opinions, preferences, and suggestions to refine and improve your brand's offerings.</p>





















  
  














































  

    

      <figure data-test="image-block-v2-outer-wrapper" class="
            sqs-block-image-figure
            image-block-outer-wrapper
            image-block-v2
            design-layout-card
            combination-animation-site-default
            individual-animation-site-default
            individual-text-animation-site-default
            image-position-right
            
          " data-scrolled
      >

        
          
            
            
              
              
              
              
              
              
              
              <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/1702913594443-SDPITUCDPUJFWG2S702L/image-asset.jpeg" data-image-dimensions="1875x2500" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/1702913594443-SDPITUCDPUJFWG2S702L/image-asset.jpeg?format=1000w" width="1875" height="2500" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/1702913594443-SDPITUCDPUJFWG2S702L/image-asset.jpeg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/1702913594443-SDPITUCDPUJFWG2S702L/image-asset.jpeg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/1702913594443-SDPITUCDPUJFWG2S702L/image-asset.jpeg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/1702913594443-SDPITUCDPUJFWG2S702L/image-asset.jpeg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/1702913594443-SDPITUCDPUJFWG2S702L/image-asset.jpeg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/1702913594443-SDPITUCDPUJFWG2S702L/image-asset.jpeg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/1702913594443-SDPITUCDPUJFWG2S702L/image-asset.jpeg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

              
            
          
            
          

        

        
          
          <figcaption data-width-ratio class="image-card-wrapper">
            

              
                <h4><strong>7. Tap into the Power of Influencer Marketing</strong></h4>
              

              
                <p class="">Collaborating with influencers who align with your brand's values and target audience can be a cost-effective way to raise brand awareness and drive sales. Seek out micro-influencers or niche-specific influencers who have a genuine connection with their followers. By leveraging their reach, you can amplify your brand's message without the price tag of traditional advertising.</p>
              

              

            
          </figcaption>
        

      </figure>

    

  





  <h4><strong>8. Leverage User-Generated Content</strong></h4><p class="">Encourage your customers to create content featuring your products or brand. User-generated content not only showcases your brand in an authentic way but also reduces the need for expensive professional photography or videography. Run contests, encourage reviews, and create a community of brand advocates who will help spread the word about your business.<br><br></p><p class="">With a dash of ingenuity, a dollop of elbow grease, and these nine tips, you're well-equipped to make a splash in the business world. This DIY journey isn't just about saving money – it's about gaining a deep understanding of your brand and its potential. When the time comes to level up with a professional designer, you'll be ready and raring to go. So, don't wait any longer. Start building that dream brand of yours!</p><p class="">Remember, a tight budget doesn't mean compromising on quality. It's about being smart, creative, and resourceful. Your brand journey starts now –  make it awesome!</p>]]></content:encoded><media:content type="image/jpeg" url="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/1702914644136-J2WPIM62SNUZTXCQVKWU/RGHENTW.jpg?format=1500w" medium="image" isDefault="true" width="1500" height="1000"><media:title type="plain">8 Tips for Building a Memorable Brand on a Budget</media:title></media:content></item><item><title>A New Chapter for Your Business: Brand Refresh Strategies for 2024</title><dc:creator>Ruta Kisonaite</dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 06:00:00 +0000</pubDate><link>https://www.socialgizmodesigns.com/blog/a-new-chapter-for-your-business-brand-refresh-strategies-for-2024</link><guid isPermaLink="false">635172c6202bb8078a469eda:639c95b6ef55106912bd2d6d:658179b93b58354f9e1e28b4</guid><description><![CDATA[As the New Year approaches, it's a time of reflection and anticipation. 
