  <h4>The Role of Packaging in Branding</h4><p class="">Packaging is often the first tangible interaction a customer has with your brand. It sets the tone for the customer experience and plays a crucial role in shaping the perception of your brand. A well-designed packaging can elevate your brand, make your product stand out on the shelves, and create a memorable unboxing experience that customers will want to share.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
