  <h4>Neglecting Market Research</h4><p class=""><strong>Disaster</strong>: One of the common mistakes startups make is not giving enough attention to conducting thorough market research. It's important to have a deep understanding of your target audience, their pain points, and preferences in order to create a brand that truly connects with them.</p><p class=""><strong>Tip</strong>: It's highly recommended to allocate time and resources for comprehensive market research. You can conduct surveys, interviews, and competitor analysis to gather valuable insights. This data will serve as a solid foundation for developing your brand strategy.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/77c3b357-ca07-4137-9065-4ff95478a7e8/9.png" data-image-dimensions="3000x2000" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/77c3b357-ca07-4137-9065-4ff95478a7e8/9.png?format=1000w" width="3000" height="2000" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/77c3b357-ca07-4137-9065-4ff95478a7e8/9.png?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/77c3b357-ca07-4137-9065-4ff95478a7e8/9.png?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/77c3b357-ca07-4137-9065-4ff95478a7e8/9.png?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/77c3b357-ca07-4137-9065-4ff95478a7e8/9.png?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/77c3b357-ca07-4137-9065-4ff95478a7e8/9.png?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/77c3b357-ca07-4137-9065-4ff95478a7e8/9.png?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/635172c6202bb8078a469eda/77c3b357-ca07-4137-9065-4ff95478a7e8/9.png?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
          
