          </figcaption>
        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <h4>Neglecting Online Presence</h4><p class=""><strong>Disaster</strong>: In today's digital age, it's crucial for a startup to prioritize its online presence. A poorly designed or outdated website, inactive social media profiles, or inconsistent online messaging can discourage potential customers.</p><p class=""><strong>Tip:</strong> Make sure to invest in a professional website, regularly update your social media profiles, and actively engage with your audience online. Take advantage of digital marketing strategies to boost your brand visibility.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
